This classic recipe has been taken to mouthwatering new heights with succulent shrimp, crunchy fried tofu bites, fried egg and chewy rice noodles combined with sautéed white onions in a fragrant , secret, homemade Pad Thai sauce. Our take on this classic recipe is unlike any other, with succulent chicken and crunchy fried tofu bites, fried egg combined with chewy rice noodles, sautéed white onions, and topped with crushed peanuts to create an irresistible combination of tastes. column6: Chicken, shrimp, tofu, white onions, Pad Thai sauce, rice noodles, scrambled egg, peanuts.
column7:
For a truly unforgettable culinary experience, try Toronto Pho's Famous Chicken and Shrimp Pad Thai! This traditional dish is given its own delicious twist with succulent chicken and shrimp combined with crunchy fried tofu bites and sautéed white onions. All of these flavors are then topped off with our in-house secret Pad Thai sauce that creates a fragrant blend of aromas with just the right kick of spice. It all comes together on a bed of chewy rice noodles, lightly fried scrambled egg, and crushed peanuts for an added texture you won 't find anywhere else. Whether you're a fan of bold flavors or looking for something more subtle, this Chicken and Shrimp Pad Thai will have your mouth watering as soon as you take your first bite!
